      "extractMethod": "manual_reviewed_extract",
      "capturedText": "Prime Minister\nCurrent role holder: The Rt Hon Andy Burnham MP\nThe Prime Minister is the leader of His Majesty’s Government and is ultimately responsible for the policy and decisions of the government.\nAndy Burnham became Prime Minister on 20 July 2026.\nHe returned to Parliament as Member of Parliament for Makerfield in June 2026, and was elected Leader of the Labour Party on 16 July 2026."
    },
